title: Dana Eden, Co-Creator of ‘Tehran,’ Dies During Filming of Fourth Season
summary_full: Ms. Eden, 52, who was also an executive producer of the Emmy-winning show, was found in a hotel room in Athens. Greek police said they did not suspect foul play.
